@Backend_APIs_HostAddress = http://192.168.100.111:5280
@AuthToken = 

# Health
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/health
Accept: application/json

###

##### Authentication

### Register
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890"
}

###

### Verify OTP
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

###

### Login
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Current user (requires Authorization)
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/current-user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Forgot password
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

### Reset password
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "token-from-email",
  "password": "NewPassword123!"
}

###

### Resend OTP
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/auth/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

##### Users

### Get my profile
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/users/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Update my profile
PUT {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Updated Name",
  "phoneNumber": "9876543210",
  "address": "123 Main St"
}

###

### Change password
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/users/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "currentPassword": "Password123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

###

### Upload profile photo (form)
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/users/upload-photo
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="profile.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

[binary data]
------WebKitFormBoundary--

###

##### Doctors

### Get all doctors
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors
Accept: application/json

###

### Get doctor by id
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get doctors by specialization
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/specialization/cardiology
Accept: application/json

###

### Update availability (requires role)
PATCH {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/1/availability
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

true

###

### Update doctor profile (requires role)
PUT {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "specialization": "General",
  "qualification": "MBBS",
  "experience": 5,
  "experienceYears": 10
}

###

### Get available doctors
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/available
Accept: application/json

###

### Search doctors
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/search?query=smith&specialization=cardiology&availableOnly=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Get specializations
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/specializations
Accept: application/json

###

### Get available slots for a doctor
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/1/available-slots?date=2026-02-16
Accept: application/json

###

### Get doctor's schedule
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/doctors/1/schedule
Accept: application/json

###

##### Appointments

### Book appointment
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "patientId": "1",
  "doctorId": "1",
  "dateTime": "2026-02-20T10:00:00Z",
  "symptoms": "Headache",
  "notes": ""
}

###

### Get student upcoming appointments
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/student/1/upcoming
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Get faculty/doctor appointments (requires role)
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/Faculty/appointments
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Get appointment by id
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Update appointment status (requires role)
PUT {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "status": "Confirmed"
}

###

### Cancel appointment
DELETE {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Add prescription (requires role)
PUT {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1/prescription
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "prescription": "Take Paracetamol 500mg twice daily"
}

###

##### Medicine Reminders

### Get my reminders
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Get active reminders
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/active
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Get reminder by id
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Create reminder
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "medicineName": "Ibuprofen",
  "dosage": "200mg",
  "frequency": "Daily",
  "times": "08:00,20:00",
  "startDate": "2026-02-16",
  "notes": "After meal"
}

###

### Update reminder
PUT {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "medicineName": "Ibuprofen",
  "dosage": "400mg",
  "frequency": "Daily",
  "times": "08:00,20:00",
  "startDate": "2026-02-16",
  "notes": ""
}

###

### Toggle reminder active
PATCH {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Delete reminder
DELETE {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### Log intake
POST {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/1/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

{
  "scheduledTime": "2026-02-16T08:00:00Z",
  "status": "taken",
  "notes": "Took with water"
}

###

### Today's schedule
GET {{Backend_APIs_HostAddress}}/api/medicinereminders/today
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###
